        id: "green-canada-corporation-announces-proposed-going-public-transaction-and-concurr",
        title: "Green Canada Corporation Announces Proposed Going Public Transaction and Concurrent Acquisition of Marshall Uranium Project from Basin Energy Limited",
        date: "November 24, 2025",
