        summary: "Toronto, Ontario, February 7, 2024 &#8211; Platinex Inc. (CSE: PTX) (OTCQB: PANXF, Frankfurt: 9PX) (“Platinex” or the “Company”) is pleased to announce results from its mechanized stripping and channe...",
