        summary: "Toronto, Ontario, November 09, 2023 – Platinex Inc. (CSE: PTX) (OTCQB: PANXF, Frankfurt: 9PX) (“Platinex” or the “Company”) is pleased to announce results from its exploration program on the Heenan Pr...",
