        category: "Corporate",
        summary: "Toronto, Ontario, March 14, 2022 &#8211; Platinex Inc. (CSE: PTX) (Frankfurt 9PX) (the &#8220;Company&#8221; or &#8220;Platinex&#8220;) is pleased to announce the appointment of Sam Kiri, CFA to the c...",
