        summary: "TORONTO, January 27, 2022 &#8211; Platinex Inc. (CSE: PTX) (Frankfurt: 9PX) (“Platinex” or the “Company”) is pleased to announce that its wholly owned subsidiary, Endurance Elements Inc. (“Endurance E...",
