        summary: "TORONTO, January 17, 2022 &#8211; Platinex Inc. (CSE: PTX) (Frankfurt 9PX) (“Platinex” or the “Company”) is pleased to announce that it has closed the acquisition of a 100% ownership interest in the W...",
